Everybody, hello.
I returned yesterday from a state visit to Portugal. I wanted to share with you some of the beauties there.
Lisbon is a European capital known for its similarity to Istanbul.
Lisbon also has seven hills, bridges and a history full of history. http://t.co/faqbfxhwhg
Portuguese explorers are famous for their oceanic discoveries. Discovered many places from India to Brazil.
They protect their Imperial glory in all their ceremonies. http://t.co/md55ha7gf3
President Silva and his wife welcomed us with a ceremony. http://t.co/rwgrkaem Up
http://t.co/s3foh9gj Up
I visited the historical parliament building with all members of the parliament. http://t.co/yzhzfnyaww
Lisbon Mayor is a very popular president. In the historic municipal court, he gave the key of Lisbon to the ceremony. http://t.co/fyhsg7shj9
He also surprised us. The Portuguese children who learned Turkish in school welcomed us by talking Turkish. http://t.co/1g1swq8oz9
I went to Portugal with a large number of Turkish businessmen.
We participated in the Turkish-Portuguese Business Forum with President Silva, and we encouraged businessmen to reciprocate. http://t.co/xr9q1udesj
The cultural program we have organized in one of the important palaces of Lisbon, with the Portuguese President and his wife ...
... a lot of Portuguese people joined. During the program, Dilek Turkkan from the Presidency Turkish Music Choir "With Üsküdar ..." ...
... together he portrays the famous Fado music of Portuguese and likes it very much. http://t.co/a1xotkpnod
The Andalusian Islamic civilization, along with Portugal, ruled for centuries in Spain and the Iberian peninsula.

In the palaces, especially the traces of the Turkish mariners are portrayed with great care in the ceiling decorations.
Nevertheless, we have faced the seas in the past. http://t.co/qgvrggoe2k
